data.description: Great opportunity to buy a 3 bed, 2 bath home with an attached mother-in-law suite/apartment. This property is perfect for an owner to occupy the main home and rent the apartment for extra income. It is also ideal for an investor looking to add to their portfolio of rentals. The main home features a large living room with great natural light. The kitchen/dining is spacious with a back porch right out the door. The master bedroom is large with an ensuite full bathroom and private back patio. The attached studio apartment is equipped with a full kitchen and bathroom with a fenced in patio for privacy. This large lot has a huge fenced in back yard with a storage shed. It currently generates $2,075 in rental income. Main home is occupied until 11/24/2023 and the apartment is month to month.
